latestIgtvVideos.title: HOPE
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
2020 has been existential central to say the very least. I personally don’t remember the last time I went to sleep without being pained by flashes of some tragedy in some part of the world (and this is my privilege). Natural disasters, war, racism, starvation, displacement, pandemic, protest, violence; it just doesn’t end. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣
And while there’s much we can do and must do; by spreading awareness, speaking for those who don’t have a voice and contributing to causes we believe in; I for one really feel like we can also use a little positivity while navigating ourselves through these trying times. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
So here’s my little attempt at spreading a little hope - and stirring a little reflection. It’s important that we see the world for how it is, but imagine it for all that it can be. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
What do I do? I turn to books sometimes, movies more often but people most of all.⁣⁣⁣⁣
I found myself faced with a question one time, “Imagine if you were the only person on Earth; would you have any desire to do anything?” And genuinely, I would not. So I turn to you all, to ask you, to turn to each other and @humansofpositiveenergy is a space I have created to do just this.⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
Do I have a plan for this page? No not really. But write in, share your thoughts, your dreams, your feelings, a poem, a painting and I hope to use your hopes to make this page prettier, and all our voices to make our futures, slightly brighter. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣
P.S. Feeling immense love for all these incredible people from all over the globe who I had the privilege of going to @royalholloway with, who continue to inspire me everyday. Also for my insanely talented brother @veerpinto, thanks for the edit child. ⁣⁣⁣⁣
